  "description": "# Busan (30km×30km)\r\n\r\n### PUS3 · v0.1.0\r\n\r\nCustom map of Busan, Korea made with official Korean traffic volume data from official soures.\r\nWith 6,968 Pops and 1,122,363 population\r\n\r\n## Coverage\r\n\r\n\u003ctable style=\"width: auto\"\u003e\r\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRegion\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eBusan, Yangsan, Gimhae \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ePlayable Area\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e900 km²\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n\u003c/table\u003e\r\n\r\n## Population Summary\r\n\r\n\u003ctable style=\"width: auto\"\u003e\r\n\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTotal Modeled Demand\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd align=\"right\"\u003e1,122,363\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\r\n\u003c/table\u003e\r\n\r\n## Additional Features\r\n\r\n- **Neighborhood Labels** — The map includes municipal and neighborhood labels derived from administrative boundary data.\r\n\t- 시도 (Si, Do - Metropolitan / Provincial level)\r\n\t- 시군구 (Si, Gun, Gu - City / County / District level)\r\n\t- 읍면동 (Eup, Myeon, Dong - Neighborhood level)\r\n\r\n## Data Sources\r\n\r\n- Korean Transportation Database (Korea Transport Institute, KOTI) (ktdb.go.kr)\r\n- V-world (Ministry of Land, Infrastructure and Transport, MOLIT) (vworld.kr)\r\n- Statistical Geographic Information System (SGIS) plus (Ministry of Data and Statistics, MODS) (sgis.mods.go.kr)\r\n- Address-based Industry Support Service (Ministry of the Interior and Safety, MOIS) (business.juso.go.kr)\r\n\r\n## Credits\r\n\r\nMap authored by Budha",
